#. Path = m_TitleText
msgctxt "9a257e9d-98e4-4490-a98d-104eebdcc26f"
msgid "Spontaneous Spellcasting"
msgstr "임의 시전"

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_SpontaneousPriest
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_DescriptionText
msgctxt "7546c2f3-288a-4167-a52b-151bd9b902f1"
msgid ""
"Some classes (such as cleric and druid) have the ability of spontaneous "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spellcasting{/g}. For example, a "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Alignment}good{/g} cleric has no need to prepare "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Healing}healing{/g} spells: they can lose almost any spell "
"they have prepared (except the domain spells) to cast a cure wounds spell of "
"the same level. In the same way, an evil cleric can lose prepared spells to "
"cast inflict wounds."
msgstr ""
"일부 직업(예: 성직자, 드루이드)은 자발적인 {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}주문 "
"시전{/g} 능력을 가지고 있습니다. 예를 들어, 선한 성직자는 "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Healing}치유{/g} 주문을 준비할 필요가 없습니다. 같은 레벨의 "
"상처 치료 주문을 시전하기 위해 준비한 거의 모든 주문(권역 주문 제외)을 잃을 "
"수 있습니다. 같은 방식으로 사악한 성직자도 준비된 주문을 잃고 상처를 입히는 "
"주문을 시전할 수 있습니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_SpontaneousPriest
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_TriggerText
msgctxt "113ca465-f372-4163-97f0-39d926428c73"
msgid ""
"Character {t|SourceUnit} is going to prepare the "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Healing}healing{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} "
"{t|SourceAbility}, even though they already can cast it spontaneously by "
"losing any other prepared spell."
msgstr ""
"캐릭터 {t|SourceUnit}은 {g|Encyclopedia:Healing}회복{/g} "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Spell}주문{/g} {t|SourceAbility}을(를) 준비하지만, 이미 "
"준비된 다른 주문을 잃음으로써 자발적으로 시전할 수 있습니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_Swarm
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_DescriptionText
msgctxt "3862051b-11d8-4f92-ba14-e37d43f55bef"
msgid ""
"Against such enemies, regular weapons are ineffective, or even completely "
"useless. However, any swarm is vulnerable to "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attacks{/g} that hit an area.\n"
"On {g|Encyclopedia:DC}difficulty{/g} levels below \"Core rules\" you can hit "
"a swarm with a regular weapon, but the {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} it "
"receives will be halved."
msgstr ""
"이러한 적에게는 일반 무기는 효과가 없거나 전혀 쓸모가 없습니다. 하지만 모든 "
"떼는 특정 지역을 공격하는 {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}공격{/g}에 취약합니다.\n"
"\"핵심 규칙\" 이하의 {g|Encyclopedia:DC}난이도{/g} 레벨에서는 일반 무기로 "
"떼를 공격할 수 있지만, 받는 {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}피해{/g}가 절반으로 "
"감소합니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_Swarm
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_SolutionNotFoundText
msgctxt "1838338c-a02e-4e17-b52c-9456b0cfdb69"
msgid ""
"Use {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attacks{/g} that hit an area, such as explosive "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spells{/g} or alchemist's fire."
msgstr ""
"폭발성 {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}주문{/g}이나 연금술사의 화염과 같이 특정 지역을 "
"타격하는 {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}공격{/g}을 사용합니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_Swarm
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_SolutionFoundText
msgctxt "ebcd49b7-5b28-4cb0-9740-5ecdb635c942"
msgid "Against a swarm of enemies, use this:"
msgstr "적 떼를 상대로 이걸 사용하세요."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_Swarm
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_TitleText
msgctxt "6aab48b1-f5f1-4067-be9b-1ed2e43a065b"
msgid "Swarm"
msgstr "스웜"

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_Swarm
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_TriggerText
msgctxt "5dea98b5-e52c-4d23-8b75-419f86dcbf8c"
msgid "You have engaged a hostile swarm {t|SourceUnit}."
msgstr "적군 무리 {t|SourceUnit}와 교전했습니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_TargetType
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_DescriptionText
msgctxt "c964673f-94e5-4666-92fe-d96d36b920f9"
msgid ""
"Some {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spells{/g} can only be cast on certain targets. "
"For example, the {g|SpellsHoldPerson}Hold Person{/g} spell must be cast on a "
"humanoid. However, there are many enemies that may have the appearance of a "
"humanoid but are, in fact, otherworldly creatures or other types of "
"creatures."
msgstr ""
"일부 {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}주문{/g}은 특정 대상에게만 시전할 수 있습니다. "
"예를 들어, {g|SpellsHoldPerson}사람 포박{/g} 주문은 반드시 휴머노이드에게 "
"발동해야 합니다. 하지만 휴머노이드의 외형을 하고 있지만 실제로는 이계의 "
"생물이나 다른 유형의 생명체인 적도 많습니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_TargetType
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_SolutionNotFoundText
msgctxt "215ac653-398c-4c4a-8c14-035871839e21"
msgid ""
"If you cannot seem to cast a certain {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} on a "
"target, try checking its type with the Inspect feature."
msgstr ""
"대상에게 특정 {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}주문{/g}을 시전할 수 없는 것 같다면, "
"검사 기능으로 해당 주문의 유형을 확인해 보세요."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_TargetType
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_TitleText
msgctxt "50b157d1-fc27-427d-af19-1c4f45378215"
msgid "Target Types"
msgstr "대상 유형"

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_TargetType
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_TriggerText
msgctxt "ef728085-6ae0-4694-8517-89ef1c2acd4b"
msgid ""
"You are trying to cast {t|SourceAbility} on an invalid target: "
"{t|TargetUnit}."
msgstr "잘못된 대상인 {t|SourceAbility}에 {t|TargetUnit}을(를) 캐스팅하려고 합니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_TouchAC
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_DescriptionText
msgctxt "ea57eff6-1033-48d5-aa19-6351ad438b3f"
msgid ""
"There are many {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spells{/g} and abilities that your "
"armor won't protect you against: to work, they need to just touch the "
"target. This is the {g|Encyclopedia:TouchAttack}touch attack{/g}, it ignores "
"armor and shields. A creature's {g|Encyclopedia:Touch_AC}touch AC{/g} is "
"usually lower than their full {g|Encyclopedia:Armor_Class}AC{/g}, as it "
"doesn't include the {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonuses{/g} from the armor, "
"natural armor, and shields.\n"
"Touch attacks can be made both in melee and from a distance (ray).\n"
"In most cases, the larger a creature is, the bigger the difference between "
"its full AC and touch AC."
msgstr ""
"방어구가 보호하지 못하는 {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}주문{/g}과 능력이 많이 "
"있는데, 이 주문과 능력이 효과를 발휘하려면 대상을 "
"{g|Encyclopedia:TouchAttack}접촉{/g}해야 합니다. 이 접촉은 "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Attack}공격{/g}이며, 갑옷과 보호막을 무시합니다. 생물의 "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Touch_AC}접촉 AC{/g}은 방어구, 자연 갑옷 보너스, 방패의 "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}보너스{/g}를 포함하지 않으므로 일반적으로 전체 "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Armor_Class}AC{/g}보다 낮습니다.\n"
"접촉 공격은 근접 공격과 원거리 공격(광선)이 모두 가능합니다.\n"
"대부분의 경우, 생물이 클수록 전체 AC과 접촉 AC의 차이가 커집니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_TouchAC
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_SolutionFoundText
msgctxt "3d621da7-0687-4508-9a71-b286c249c3fa"
msgid "To increase your combat efficiency, try using this:"
msgstr "전투 효율을 높이려면 이걸 사용해 보세요."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_TouchAC
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_SolutionNotFoundText
msgctxt "cd01f886-2d14-4e3e-a21f-4e100df43b0f"
msgid ""
"When you fight an enemy with a low {g|Encyclopedia:Touch_AC}touch AC{/g}, "
"use combat {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spells{/g}."
msgstr ""
"낮은 {g|Encyclopedia:TouchAttack}접촉{/g}을 가진 적과 싸울 때 "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Armor_Class}AC{/g}, 전투 {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}주문{/g}을 "
"사용합니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_TouchAC
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_TitleText
msgctxt "25e3f0ad-44a6-46b7-841f-fba36050f0ad"
msgid "Touch AC"
msgstr "접촉 AC"

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_TouchAC
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_TriggerText
msgctxt "f3a7a5ab-0351-4b4d-aaf2-7f70aa35edaa"
msgid "You frequently miss the enemy {t|TargetUnit}."
msgstr "적 {t|TargetUnit}을 자주 놓칩니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_WeaponPlusFive
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
#. Path = m_TriggerText
msgctxt "ab8a4c57-3aec-4d6b-ad97-4aeaeaa6a981"
msgid ""
"You have received an item: {t|SourceItem}. It can bypass "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Reduction}damage reduction{/g} N/"
"{g|Encyclopedia:Alignment}alignment{/g}, N/adamantine, or N/cold iron "
"despite not being made from the right material or enchanted."
msgstr ""
"아이템 획득: {t|SourceItem}. 이 아이템은 {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Reduction}"
"피해 감소{/g}를 우회할 수 있습니다. 올바른 재료로 만들지 않았거나 마법이 "
"부여되지 않았더라도 N/{g|Encyclopedia:Alignment}성향{/g}, N/아다만틴 또는 N/"
"냉철을 무시할 수 있습니다."

#. File = Tutorials/ContextTutorial/ContextTutor_WeaponPlusFive
#. Type = Kingmaker.Tutorial.BlueprintTutorial
