msgctxt "35a3ce9f-200a-4711-9011-9bb5448f1845"
msgid ""
"You can now control armies on the global map. Winning battles against demon "
"forces provides a number of benefits, such as:\n"
"* Resources to help your economy.\n"
"* Relics, which can be turned into powerful new items for your party.\n"
"* Captured enemy fortifications that previously blocked the advance of your "
"party and your armies. These fortifications can be rebuilt into forts for "
"your own troops.\n"
"Enemy armies differ in their strength, which is displayed as a number next "
"to the army's name. By hovering over the enemy army, you can learn more "
"about its composition and the reward it is guarding."
