"the banners at the top of the screen.\n"
"In army command mode, you can select armies by either using the panel on the "
"left or clicking the figures on the map.\n"
"Much like your party, armies use roads to move around the map. To move, an "
"army must spend movement points, which can be restored by resting for one "
"day."
msgstr ""
"화면 상단의 배너를 클릭하여 파티 관리 모드와 군대 지휘 모드를 전환할 수 "
"있습니다.\n"
